165
00:13:01,846 --> 00:13:04,727
[SPEAKER_01]: And so it was a treat.

166
00:13:04,767 --> 00:13:07,329
[SPEAKER_01]: And my wife helped start the museum store,

167
00:13:08,169 --> 00:13:11,311
[SPEAKER_01]: And so it's rare that she and I got to do things together.

168
00:13:11,831 --> 00:13:18,016
